- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper introduces a new automaton model for data words. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of registers in the automaton model. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper proves the equivalence of different automaton models. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) may be relevant as the paper deals with the recognition of languages. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) may be relevant as the paper introduces a new model for language recognition.
